	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">As I already said on my guild website, I am no longer going straight for manaburn because quite frankly I can do more damage with nukes + crits in 1 minute than I could ever do with manaburn.</font></p>
	
