	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" color="#FFFFFF"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">I think Verant is probably pretty annoyed with the whole Mana Burn issue. On prexus, as on many other servers, we have a Mana Burn team... I've already experienced first hand losing a mob to these guys... <br />
<br />
It's no fun. You mobilize your guild and pull together efforts to take down a mob, in this case it was Gore, only to be beaten by a bunch of robe-wearing crossdressers /grin<br />
<br />
I think the changes Verant are incorporating are probably long overdue, and needed to balance the gameplay back to what the idea once was. It's a shock to many, myself inclucded, and my initial response was a more negative one. As long as they adjust the mobs, so we don't end up with a scenario where only the mightiest of guilds on servers can take down the best mobs... That would defeat the purpose of making it fun, as Verant stated they wanted to make it.</font></p>
	
