	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">What about the CHeal changes guys!?!<br />
<br />
For most practical situations it is not a big deal to have the HP cap lowered to 7500.  Howeer, with the new PoP - we can expect to see people approach the the 10,000 HP cap.<br />
<br />
So what do we have ...<br />
<br />
*biff*  CLR lose the Res monopoly <br />
<br />
*kick*  CLR lose 10% heal differential<br />
<br />
*smack* CLR have to face CHeal-lite from DRU SHM<br />
<br />
*punch* CLR have the CHeal nerfed<br />
<br />
What have we gained ...<br />
<br />
*groan* We can Bash with our shields<br />
<br />
*wheeze*  We can smack things with a new hammer while we get hammered ourselves<br />
<br />
*cheer* We can let off a mighty Yaulp<br />
<br />
... most of this you can't touch till 56<br />
<br />
I pity anyone building a low/mid cleric - the road has been getting alot tougher of late <img src="images/smilies/orangesad.gif" border="0" alt=""><br />
