	<font face="verdana,arial,helvetica" size="1" color="#FFFFFF"> <b></b></font>
	<p><font face="verdana, arial, helvetica" size="2" color="#FFFFFF">There is a new evil force throughout the land - it is called Verant/Sony.<br />
<br />
This new evil, this new threat, is causing a relative withering of the CLR class.<br />
<br />
My guess is that it is a secret conspiracy of evil-Druids lead by the elusive leader of this class - "Evil Elvis"  (ever wondered how come he is spotted at all those gas stations - he can TP - he is a Druid).<br />
<br />
He has been craving CLR like heals to complete his quest for world domination.  AND HE HAS SUCCEEDED!!  Using "animal charm" spells he has entranced Verant developers (see, again, he must be a Druid) into working his wicked changes into subsequent patches.<br />
<br />
His followers are impervious to rational debate (some sort of "Skin like Jackass" spell - must be a Druid).<br />
<br />
His only weakness is that he leaves Druid dropping trails of foraged Candy bar and fast food wrappers.  We need to use this to TRACK HIM DOWN AND BASH HIM WITH OUR SHIELDS!</font></p>
	
